Ther Places where we can store the data is Storage Area


Storage Area:

1. Temporary Storage Areas  --> All JVM memory areas are temporary Storage Areas. Once the JVM Shuts Down, all data s are gone 
2. Permanent Storage Areas  --> Persistant storage Areas

From JAVA Application, the technology used to communicate with database is JDBC

JDBC is a specification


JAVA Vendor provide this specification.
database Vendors like oracle implements datatbase vendor



Features of JDBC

1. Standart API, means never going to change database to database, means same format